  "body": "In several places in the code, we allow @truffle/db capabilities to be opt-in in via two mechanisms:\r\n- @truffle/db is an external, optional dependency of Truffle, so it might fail to import\r\n- Users must enable it via `db: { enabled: true }` in their truffle-config.js.\r\n\r\nAs a result, there's a bunch of repetition in the codebase for making sure these conditions are met.\r\n\r\nThese should get cleaned up into something concise+canonical.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @cds-amal in https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/pull/3898#discussion_r585147302_",
